						               													<description>This is an Advanced Tobruk module detailing the bitter fighting around Ia Drang, Vietnam, in November 1965.  In this module the men and weapons of the 7th Air Cavalry face stiff opposition from NVA regulars in a series of scenarios that depict the Americans' landing in the &amp;quot;Hot LZ&amp;quot; and the subsequent battles with an entire NVA battalion in extremely difficult and unfamiliar terrain.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;ATS fans will find new weapons such as &amp;quot;thumper&amp;quot; grenade launchers, M60 machine guns and, best of all, a brace of Huey helicopter types and new rules to implement their use.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This set is a remastering of a previous release, LZ X-Ray, with cardstock map panels and new counters.  The module is available in two versions: one with only the new maps &amp;amp; scenarios for owners of ATS: Hue, and a &amp;quot;full&amp;quot; version that adds the required combat counters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
